{"tid":872603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬼] 加拿大在美核潛艇基地附近放置中國產高科技監測設備","createTime":"2018-10-22T23:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T08:54:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39fd1a78e44ea29eafe708dcf80d63294e216bd3","tid":872603,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T23:48:12.000Z","msg":"加拿大在美核潛艇基地附近放置中國產高科技監測設備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/canada-installs-chinese-underwater-monitoring-devices-next-to-us-nuclear-submarine-base-20181022/4624122.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fcanada-installs-chinese-underwater-monitoring-devices-next-to-us-nuclear-submarine-base-20181022%2F4624122.html&d=HDdcVWKqnhaKed%2FWU9HMkDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f5c66fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/canada-installs-chinese-underwater-monitoring-devices-next-to-us-nuclear-submarine-base-20181022/4624122.html</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大在美國太平洋海岸外僅300公里的一處海域放置了4個中國產的高科技海洋監測設備。該海域附近有一個美國的核潛艇基地。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》和總部設在北京的中國網絡媒體《財經時報》星期一都報導說，根據一項加拿大的科研機構&ldquo;加拿大海洋網路&rdquo;和中國的合作項目，加拿大海岸防衛隊今年6月將這些高科技設備放置在胡安德富卡海嶺，以監測水下環境。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;加拿大海洋網路&rdquo;由加拿大維多利亞大學負責管理，但這4個設備屬於中國科學院三亞深海科學與工程研究所，其所收集到數據也可實時傳送到中國。<br />\n</span><br />\n兩家媒體都報導說，&ldquo;加拿大海洋網路&rdquo;已證實在網路內放置中國產的裝備。美國國務院不願對《南華早報》的報導給予任何置評。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有證據顯示，中國軍方參與了這個項目，但《南華早報》說，這些裝置所蒐集的資料將有助於中國了解美國附近的戰略航道環境，甚至用來追踪潛艇或其他軍艦。</span>"},{"pid":"cc1dd31b951d977dd5c1e38f075dafb1104aecb8","tid":872603,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T23:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e979f3f593053511b3fd5ad9164ebd104f3661","tid":872603,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:20:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2604ee25d8b9c2152565a2a24338177bbfe677","tid":872603,"uid":177047,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"加拿大叛變，左癌冚家鏟快d仆街死"},{"pid":"0a56a7b504199ed7793a6ec2d71388e87f1a934a","tid":872603,"uid":20563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e2604ee25d8b9c2152565a2a24338177bbfe677","tid":872603,"uid":177047,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"加拿大叛變，左癌冚家鏟快d仆街死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"紅早都叛變喎，俾tips 美國佬"},{"pid":"cd191ad4d1ae2dd2624a74d4c6e721fd50afd703","tid":872603,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"左膠上場問題，以前右派做主流，個到租比美軍練射魚雷，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5310f34bdfdc1f62906bbf1f5a940660dadc05f0","tid":872603,"uid":79370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"不怕神一般的對手，只怕豬一般的隊友。"},{"pid":"88d510ceb8b1afd97a1cb822cc3e9e58c88fb601","tid":872603,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd191ad4d1ae2dd2624a74d4c6e721fd50afd703","tid":872603,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"左膠上場問題，以前右派做主流，個到租比美軍練射魚雷，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2e6e0f5ee7f8ad094de0c9f96daabdd9622f72","tid":872603,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"美國佬一野唔出聲就炸撚左佢"},{"pid":"199d74cec20f363a135cc7e443db69010c2187a1","tid":872603,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T00:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa